<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>LifeLink</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/homepage.css" />
</head>
<body>
  
    <main class="main-content">
      <header class="top-nav">
        <h2><span class="blue">LifeLink</span><span></span></h2>
        <nav class="top-links">
          
          <div class="dropdown">
            <button class="dropdown-button blood" onclick="toggleDropdown()">LOOKING FOR BLOOD</button>
            <div class="dropdown-content" id="bloodDropdown">


              <a href="#">Blood Availability</a>
              <a href="#">Blood Bank Directory</a>
              <a href="#">Thalassemia Request</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="dropdown">
            <button class="dropdown-button blood" onclick="toggleDropdown()">LOOKING FOR Medicine</button>
            <div class="dropdown-content" id="bloodDropdown">


              <a href="#">Blood Availability</a>
              <a href="#">Blood Bank Directory</a>
              <a href="#">Thalassemia Request</a>
            </div>
          </div>


         
              
          
          <a href="#">Live Map</a>
          <a href="#">Events & Drives</a>
          <a href="#">Store</a>

          <a href="#">🌐</a>
          <a href="#">Login</a>
          <button class="top-signup">Sign Up</button>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <h1>Empowering Communities to<br><span>Save Lives & Reduce Waste</span></h1>
        <p>
          LifeLink connects donors with those in need, creating a decentralized network
          for blood and medicine exchange that saves lives and reduces medical waste.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <button class="primary-btn">Donate Now</button>
          <button class="secondary-btn">Request Help</button>
          <button class="secondary-btn">Join the Network</button>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="impact-section">
        <h2>Making a Real Impact</h2>
        <div class="stats-container">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="icon">💙</div>
            <p class="label">Lives Saved</p>
            <p class="number" data-count="1245">0</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="icon">💉</div>
            <p class="label">Donations Fulfilled</p>
            <p class="number" data-count="3782">0</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="icon">🧑‍🤝‍🧑</div>
            <p class="label">Active Volunteers</p>
            <p class="number" data-count="527">0</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
  <section class="how-it-works">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">
      LifeLink's platform makes it easy to donate or request blood and medicine with just a few steps.
    </p>

    <div class="steps-container">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="icon">🤝</div>
        <h3>Step 1: Donate</h3>
        <p>Give what you can, whether blood or medicine.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="icon">🔍</div>
        <h3>Step 2: Match</h3>
        <p>Our AI-powered system matches you with a recipient in need.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="icon">❤️</div>
        <h3>Step 3: Help</h3>
        <p>Receive or give life-saving help quickly and securely.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="community-impact">
    <h2>Community Impact</h2>
    <div class="impact-container">
      
      <!-- Testimonials -->
      <div class="testimonials">
        <h3>Testimonials</h3>

        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p><em>LifeLink helped me find a rare blood type for my mother during an emergency. I’m forever grateful for this platform.</em></p>
          <div class="user">
            <div class="avatar">M</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Michael Chen</strong><br/>
              <span>Recipient</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p><em>As a regular blood donor, LifeLink has made the process so much more meaningful. I can see the direct impact of my donations.</em></p>
          <div class="user">
            <div class="avatar">S</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Sarah Johnson</strong><br/>
              <span>Donor</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p><em>Our hospital has been able to reduce blood shortages by 40% since partnering with LifeLink. This is saving lives every day.</em></p>
          <div class="user">
            <div class="avatar">D</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Dr. Patel</strong><br/>
              <span>Hospital Partner</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Live Donation Drives -->
      <div class="donation-drives">
        <h3>Live Donation Drives</h3>

        <div class="drive-card">
          <div class="drive-header">
            <strong>Emergency Blood Drive</strong>
            <span class="tag urgent">Urgent</span>
          </div>
          <p>📅 Tomorrow, 9 AM - 5 PM<br/>📍 Central Hospital</p>
          <button>Join Drive</button>
        </div>

        <div class="drive-card">
          <div class="drive-header">
            <strong>Medicine Collection</strong>
            <span class="tag needed">Needed</span>
          </div>
          <p>📅 Next Saturday, 10 AM - 2 PM<br/>📍 Community Center</p>
          <button>Join Drive</button>
        </div>

        <div class="drive-card">
          <div class="drive-header">
            <strong>Regular Blood Donation</strong>
            <span class="tag routine">Routine</span>
          </div>
          <p>📅 May 15, 8 AM - 4 PM<br/>📍 Downtown Clinic</p>
          <button>Join Drive</button>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <script src="/js/homepage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
